+ * All JSON responses include `success: true`. For "soft success" cases
+ * (command ran but had no effect), set `effect: false` with a reason.
+ *
+ * @example
+ * // Normal success
+ * printJsonResult({ bulletId, type, newState });
+ * // → { "success": true, "bulletId": "...", "type": "...", "newState": "..." }
